 currently free on youtube/vimeo/etc.). You are more than welcome to sell/rent your work on your site, itunes, netflix, etc. without limitation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIf you have any questions or concerns, you can always contact Andrew O\'Neal at <a href=\"mailto:andrew@filmbundle.com\">andrew@filmbundle.com</a>.\r\n<div class=\"subform1\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Submission Form:</h3>\r\n[gravityform id=\"1\" name=\"Submit a Film\" title=\"false\" description=\"false\"]\r\n\r\n</div>','Your film could be included in our next bundle!','','publish','open','open','','submit','','','2012-11-15 00:28:59','2012-11-15 00:28:59','',0,'http://www.filmbundle.com/?page_id=95',0,'page','',0),(96,3,'2012-11-10 23:52:59','2012-11-10 23:52:59','','Submit A Film','','inherit','open','open','','95-revision','','','2012-11-10 23:52:59','2012-11-10 23:52:59','',95,'http://www.filmbundle.com/95-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(97,3,'2012-11-10 23:53:09','2012-11-10 23:53:09','hello','Submit A Film','','inherit','open','open','','95-revision-2','','','2012-11-10 23:53:09','2012-11-10 23:53:09','',95,'http://www.filmbundle.com/95-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(98,3,'2012-11-15 00:28:57','2012-11-15 00:28:57','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Submissions are now being accepted</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We truly want to represent the best of independent filmmaking with each and every bundle. Projects that make it into the bundles come from many sources, but in order to really reflect the spirit of indie filmmaking, we certainly can\'t overlook submissions directly from filmmakers like you.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">So why should you submit your project?</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>Exposure:</strong> Get your film in front of a whole new audience, not to mention all the publicity that our PR team can muster. Have a film that did well in festivals and now just sits on your reel? It\'s time to get that working for ya.</li>\n	<li><strong>Revenue Share:</strong> Our